<div class="px-4  ">
    <h2 class="display-4 mb-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis text-center">Return and Refund Policy</h2>
    <div class=" mb-4">
        <h2 class="lead mb-3 fw-bold">1. Initiating a Return or Exchange</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-2">
            Contact Us: To initiate a return or exchange, please contact our customer support team. Provide
            your order number and a brief description of the reason for the return.</p>
        <p class="lead mb-2">
            Return Authorization: Once your return request is approved, you will receive instructions on how to return the item(s) to us.</p>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h2 class="lead mb-3 fw-bold">2. Refunds</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-2 ">
            Refund Process: Refunds will be issued to the original payment method within [X] business days
            of receiving the returned item(s). Please note that it may take additional time for your bank or
            credit card company to process the refund.</p>
        <p class="lead mb-2 ">
            Refund Amount: The refund amount will include the purchase price of the item(s) minus any
            shipping charges (if applicable). We do not refund the original shipping cost unless the return
            is due to an error on our part.</p>

    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h2 class="lead mb-3 fw-bold">3. Shipping Costs</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-2">
            Return Shipping: Customers are responsible for return shipping costs, unless the return is due
            to a mistake on our part or a defective item.</p>
        <p class="lead mb-2">
            Exchange Shipping: If you are exchanging an item, we will cover the cost of shipping the replacement item to you.</p>
        <p class="lead mb-2">
           
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h2 class="lead mb-3 fw-bold">4. Damaged or Incorrect Items</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-2">
            Received a Damaged or Incorrect Item: If you receive a damaged or incorrect item, please contact us immediately. We will provide instructions for returning the item and will cover the return shipping costs.</p>
    </div>
</div>


